videos.headline: Pacers clobber Knicks to even series
videos.description: The Pacers get a balanced scoring effort across the board as they beat the Knicks decisively in Game 4 to even the series.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Pacers clobber Knicks to even series) 2024/05/12 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Haliburton steps into a long 3-pointer and knocks it down
videos.description: Tyrese Haliburton dribbles up and splashes home a long 3-pointer early.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Haliburton steps into a long 3-pointer and knocks it down) 2024/05/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Myles Turner hits desperation 3 as shot clock is expiring
videos.description: Myles Turner beats the shot clock with a tough 3-pointer over a defender.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Myles Turner hits desperation 3 as shot clock is expiring) 2024/05/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Obi Toppin's alley-oop dunk has Pacers fans rocking
videos.description: Obi Toppin flushes home the alley-oop dunk to put the Pacers up 23 in the first quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Obi Toppin's alley-oop dunk has Pacers fans rocking) 2024/05/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Siakam's bucket over Hartenstein forces a Knicks timeout
videos.description: Pascal Siakam finishes over Isaiah Hartenstein for a bucket and a 21-point lead.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Siakam's bucket over Hartenstein forces a Knicks timeout) 2024/05/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tyrese Haliburton takes an elbow to face on the Alec Burks and-1
videos.description: Tyrese Haliburton appears to be shaken up after taking an elbow to the face from Alec Burks on the and-1.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Tyrese Haliburton takes an elbow to face on the Alec Burks and-1) 2024/05/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Haliburton ends incredible Pacers half with a 3-pointer
videos.description: Tyrese Haliburton knocks down the 3-pointer to end a big-time first half for the Pacers.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Haliburton ends incredible Pacers half with a 3-pointer) 2024/05/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Siakam gets the steal-and-slam early in the second half
videos.description: Pascal Siakam steals the pass and takes off for a two-handed dunk early in the second half.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Siakam gets the steal-and-slam early in the second half) 2024/0512 ESHEET
